    <constitutionalAuthorityStatementText><![CDATA[<pre>By Mr. CARTWRIGHT:H.R. 5187.Congress has the power to enact this legislation pursuantto the following:Article I, Section 8, Clause 3: To regulate commerce withforeign nations, and among the several states, and with theIndian tribes;[Page H6815]</pre>]]></constitutionalAuthorityStatementText>
